{"heading":"The Saints are told to be holy, sanctify themselves, and love one another—The Lord will come, and the dead will rise.","number":4,"verseCount":18,"verses":[[1,["Furthermore then we beseech you, brethren, and exhort ",["you",["clarity-word"]]," by the Lord Jesus, that as ye have ",["received",["study-note-ref","a",[["Philip. 4:9","nt/philip/4.9"],"."]]]," of us how ye ought to ",["walk",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Walking with God","tg/walking-with-god"],"."]]]," and to ",["please",["study-note-ref","c",[["Col. 1:10","nt/col/1.10"],"."]]]," God, ",["so",["clarity-word"]]," ye would ",["abound",["study-note-ref","d",[["1 Thes. 3:12","nt/1-thes/3.12"],"."]]]," more and more."]],[2,["For ye know what commandments ",["we",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 1:38","dc-testament/dc/1.38"],"."]]]," gave you by the Lord Jesus."]],[3,["For this is the will of God, ",["even",["clarity-word"]]," your ",["sanctification",["study-note-ref","a",[["Heb. 12:14","nt/heb/12.14"],"."]]],", that ye should ",["abstain",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Abstain","tg/abstain"],"."]]]," from ",["fornication",["study-note-ref","c",["GR immorality. ",["TG Chastity","tg/chastity"],"; ",["Fornication","tg/fornication"],"; ",["Sexual Immorality","tg/sexual-immorality"],"; ",["Whore","tg/whore"],"."]]],":"]],[4,["That every one of you should know how to possess his ",["vessel",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Body, Sanctity of","tg/body-sanctity-of"],"."]]]," in ",["sanctification",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Sanctification","tg/sanctification"],"."]]]," and honour;"]],[5,["Not in the ",["lust of concupiscence",["study-note-ref","a",["GR passion of lust. ",["TG Lust","tg/lust"],"; ",["Marriage, Husbands","tg/marriage-husbands"],"."]]],", even as the ",["Gentiles",["study-note-ref","b",[["Eph. 4:17 (17, 19)","nt/eph/4.17"],"."]]]," which ",["know not",["study-note-ref","c",[["Eph. 2:12 (11–12)","nt/eph/2.12"],"."]]]," God:"]],[6,["That no ",["man",["clarity-word"]]," ",["go beyond and defraud",["study-note-ref","a",["GR take advantage of, wrong."]]]," his brother in ",["any matter",["study-note-ref","b",["GR the matter."]]],": because that the Lord ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," the ",["avenger",["study-note-ref","c",[["2 Thes. 1:8","nt/2-thes/1.8"],"."]]]," of all such, as we also have forewarned you and testified."]],[7,["For God hath not called us unto ",["uncleanness",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Uncleanness","tg/uncleanness"],"."]]],", but unto holiness."]],[8,["He therefore that ",["despiseth",["study-note-ref","a",["GR rejects, sets aside, violates."]]],", ",["despiseth",["study-note-ref","b",[["Luke 10:16","nt/luke/10.16"],"."]]]," not man, but God, who hath also given unto us his ",["holy Spirit",["study-note-ref","c",[["1 Cor. 2:10","nt/1-cor/2.10"],"; ",["1 Jn. 3:24","nt/1-jn/3.24"],"."]]],"."]],[9,["But as touching ",["brotherly love",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Brotherhood and Sisterhood","tg/brotherhood-and-sisterhood"],"."]]]," ye need not that I write unto you: for ye yourselves are ",["taught",["study-note-ref","b",[["John 6:45","nt/john/6.45"],"; ",["1 Jn. 2:27 (20, 27)","nt/1-jn/2.27"],"."]]]," of God to ",["love",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Love","tg/love"],"."]]]," one another."]],[10,["And indeed ye do it toward all the brethren which are in all Macedonia: but we beseech you, brethren, that ye increase more and more;"]],[11,["And that ye ",["study",["study-note-ref","a",["GR strive, endeavor earnestly."]]]," to be quiet, and to do your own business, and to ",["work",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Industry","tg/industry"],"; ",["Labor","tg/labor"],"; ",["Skill","tg/skill"],"; ",["Work, Value of","tg/work-value-of"],"."]]]," with your own ",["hands",["study-note-ref","c",[["Prov. 31:13","ot/prov/31.13"],"."]]],", as we commanded you;"]],[12,["That ye may walk ",["honestly",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Dependability","tg/dependability"],"; ",["Honesty","tg/honesty"],"."]]]," toward them that are without, and ",["that",["clarity-word"]]," ye may have lack of nothing."]],[13,["But I would not have you to be ignorant, brethren, concerning them which are asleep, that ye ",["sorrow",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Despair","tg/despair"],"; ",["Mourning","tg/mourning"],"; ",["Sorrow","tg/sorrow"],"."]]]," not, even as others which have no ",["hope",["study-note-ref","b",[["Eph. 2:12","nt/eph/2.12"],"."]]],"."]],[14,["For if we believe that Jesus died and rose again, even so them also which ",["sleep",["study-note-ref","a",[["Zech. 14:5","ot/zech/14.5"],"."]]]," in Jesus will God bring with him."]],[15,["For this we say unto you by the word of the Lord, ",["that",["study-note-ref","a",[["JST 1 Thes. 4:15","jst/jst-1-thes/4.15"]," … that they who are alive at the coming of the Lord, shall not prevent them who remain unto the coming of the Lord, who are asleep."]]]," ",["we",["study-note-ref","b",[["2 Thes. 2:2 (1–3)","nt/2-thes/2.2"],"."]]]," which are alive ",["and",["clarity-word"]]," remain unto the coming of the Lord shall not ",["prevent",["study-note-ref","c",["GR precede, make progress over."]]]," them which are asleep."]],[16,["For the Lord himself shall ",["descend",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Second Coming","tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"],"."]]]," from heaven with ",["a shout",["study-note-ref","b",["GR a cry of command, a cheer."]]],", with the voice of the ",["archangel",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Adam","tg/adam"],"."]]],", and with the ",["trump",["study-note-ref","d",[["Matt. 24:31","nt/matt/24.31"],"."]]]," of God: and the dead in Christ shall ",["rise",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Resurrection","tg/resurrection"],"."]]]," first:"]],[17,[["Then",["study-note-ref","a",["JST 1 Thes. 4:17 Then they who are alive, shall be caught up together into the clouds with them who remain, to meet the Lord in the air; and so shall we be ever with the Lord."]]]," we which are alive ",["and",["clarity-word"]]," remain shall be ",["caught up",["study-note-ref","b",[["1 Cor. 15:51","nt/1-cor/15.51"],"; ",["D&C 88:9